  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Events Barista",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary: </strong>Are you passionate about coffee and enjoy working in dynamic event environments? Kings Cart Coffee is looking for an enthusiastic Events Barista to join our team! In this role, you will play a key part in setting up and managing coffee cart events and ensuring smooth deliveries. If you have barista experience and a valid driving license, this could be the perfect opportunity for you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Set up and break down coffee cart equipment at events.</li>\n  <li>Handle coffee making and customer service during events.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely and safe delivery of coffee beans and equipment to event locations.</li>\n  <li>Assist in event coordination and provide support to the team as needed.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and proper upkeep of equipment during and after events.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic Barista experience is required.</li>\n  <li>Valid <strong>Class 3/3A driving license </strong>is a must.</li>\n  <li>Willing to travel to multiple locations.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and customer service skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work flexible hours, including weekends and public holidays.</li>\n  <li>Physically able to lift and transport equipment <strong>up to</strong> <strong>30KG</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 day work week</li>\n  <li>Staff Discount</li>\n  <li>Birthday Leave</li>\n  <li>Medical Benefits</li>\n  <li>Bi-Annual Bonus</li>\n  <li>Training and Uniform provided</li>\n  <li>Skill development and career progression opportunities</li>\n  <li>$1200 New Join Bonus Incentive (T&amp;C applies)</li>\n</ul>",
